About Munster

If you are in need of Pain Management Physician and Vein Specialist services in Munster, IN, Centers for Pain Control and Vein Care is here to serve you. Our office provides a variety of services, including Sclerotherapy, Sciatica, Kyphoplasty, and Chiropractic Care to our patients with care and expertise. Centers for Pain Control and Vein Care have served many happy patients of the Munster community. We hope to see you in our office soon!

Munster is located in Lake County, near the cities of Highland, IN and Lansing, IL. The city is home to a variety of schools, including Munster High School, and colleges such as Purdue University-Calumet Campus and South Suburban College. Patients of our practice can enjoy local attractions and activities in Munster such as Parc Albert Schweitzer, Eglise Catholique Saint-Léger, and Office de tourisme de la Vallée de Munster. After your appointment, grab a bite to eat at one of Munster's many lively restaurants, including Winstub S'Stewla or Restaurant a La Schlitte.
